T04TD3851E:26b-1: dzny'a na s'a ra sa mu tstsha ya n'a ma /
T04TD3851E:26b-3: ye shes snying po kun las btus pa zhes bya ba /
T04TD3851E:26b-5: dpal mgon bla ma la btud nas //
T04TD3851E:26b-6: byis rnams sdug bsngal zhi bya'i phyir //
T04TD3851E:26b-7: ye shes snying po kun las btus //
T04TD3851E:26b-9: dngos dang dngos med las grol zhing //
T04TD3851E:26b-10: dngos dang dngos med rab ldan pa //
T04TD3851E:26b-11: 'gyur ba med par grol ba'i mchog / yid kyi rang bzhin grol ba'i gnas //
T04TD3851E:26b-12: gang yin de la bsam gtan gyis //
T04TD3851E:26b-14: 'gro dang dngos po'i ngo bo rnams //
T04TD3851E:26b-15: rig pa'i ming du de brjod do //
T04TD3851E:26b-16: dngos med stong pa mkha' 'dra ba //
T04TD3851E:26b-17: yod pa rnam par spangs pa ni //
T04TD3851E:26b-18: de nyid mchog de thar 'dod rnams //
T04TD3851E:26b-19: 'khrul dang rmongs chen gnas yin no //
T04TD3851E:26b-20: re zhig dngos gang yod na ni //
T04TD3851E:26b-21: rnam par 'jig pa'i gnas la gnas //
T04TD3851E:26b-22: dngos po rnams ni med na yang //
T04TD3851E:26b-23: stong pa nyid las skye bar 'gyur //
T04TD3851E:26b-24: de phyir phyogs ni gnyis po yang //
T04TD3851E:26b-25: skems shing yongs su skems pa ni //
T04TD3851E:26b-26: mkhas pa'i go 'phang mchog phra ba //
T04TD3851E:26b-27: bla ma'i zhal la gnas pa'o //
T04TD3851E:26b-28: gang yod de kun 'di rnams 'jig / gang med de yang 'bras bu med //
T04TD3851E:26b-29: des na gnyis kyi dbus mi gnas //
T04TD3851E:26b-30: rab phra mkhas pa gang gis rtogs //
T04TD3851E:26b-31: de kho na nyid rin chen mchog / dngos po med pa nyi tshe la //
T04TD3851E:26b-32: rmongs pa rnams ni nye bar gnas //
T04TD3851E:26b-33: khong myags dman pa'i gnas la ni //
T04TD3851E:26b-34: blun po de dag 'di na gnas //
T04TD3851E:26b-35: de nyid dam pa mkha' 'dra la //
T04TD3851E:26b-36: gang dag sems ni rab rmongs pa //
T04TD3851E:27a-2: mchog tu rmongs pa dag tu 'gyur //
T04TD3851E:27a-3: dngos po nyams su myong ba yang //
T04TD3851E:27a-4: zad gnas yin pas rten med de //
T04TD3851E:27a-5: cung zad dus kyi bde thob kyi //
T04TD3851E:27a-6: rnam par grol bar mi brjod do //
T04TD3851E:27a-7: de phyir dngos yod mi bya zhing //
T04TD3851E:27a-8: dngos po med pa'i yid kyang spangs //
T04TD3851E:27a-10: de bzhin bar du'ang gnas mi bya //
T04TD3851E:27a-11: dbang phyug la sogs yon tan 'dod //
T04TD3851E:27a-12: grangs can smra rnams yon tan med //
T04TD3851E:27a-13: changs pa 'dod pa bram ze rnams //
T04TD3851E:27a-14: 'di rnams de nyid rnam gsum gnas //
T04TD3851E:27a-15: ser skya rnams ni stong pa'i tshul ;
T04TD3851E:27a-16: / dbang po thub rnams nam mkha'i tshul //
T04TD3851E:27a-17: zad byed rgyal ba'i gzugs brnyan rnams //
T04TD3851E:27a-19: dbang po lnga dang nyer ldan pa'i //
T04TD3851E:27a-20: bdag yod bram ze mchog rnams so //
T04TD3851E:27a-21: las med thar pa med kyang rung //
T04TD3851E:27a-22: gzhung ngan rgyang 'phen pa yi gzhung //
T04TD3851E:27a-23: dbang phyug pa yi bstan pa la //
T04TD3851E:27a-24: lho byang nub tu gnas pa ste //
T04TD3851E:27a-25: de yang nus can mnyam sbyor bar //
T04TD3851E:27a-26: byed cing mig ni 'dzums lta ba'o //
T04TD3851E:27a-27: zla ba'i grub mtha' pa rtag tu //
T04TD3851E:27a-28: 'phrog po la ni gus gzhol ba //
T04TD3851E:27a-29: snying ga'i pad ma'i rlung gi ni //
T04TD3851E:27a-30: rnal 'byor ldan pa'ang sgom par byed //
T04TD3851E:27a-32: de kho na zhes rtogs shing gnas //
T04TD3851E:27a-33: bden pa gang yin de nyon zhes //
T04TD3851E:27a-34: sgrub bo slob ma la smra ste //
T04TD3851E:27a-35: dbugs rgyu ba dang rab rtog med //
T04TD3851E:27a-36: yid ni gar shi bden pa'o //
T04TD3851E:27a-37: de nyid mchog de'ang gsungs pa ni //
T04TD3851E:27a-38: bdag ni dngos la rjes rmongs pa //
T04TD3851E:27a-39: gal te ye shes mi shes na //
T04TD3851E:27a-40: ye shes shin tu thal bar 'gyur //
T04TD3851E:27a-42: srid gang yin par slar 'ching ngo //
T04TD3851E:27a-43: sangs rgyas chos ni rnam pa bzhir //
T04TD3851E:27a-44: yid 'dod rnams kyis sngon mthong de //
T04TD3851E:27a-45: bye brag smra la sogs pa'i lam //
T04TD3851E:27a-46: bshad pas de nyid sgrub pa'o //
T04TD3851E:27a-47: nam mkha' 'gog pa gnyis dag ste //
T04TD3851E:27a-48: 'dus ma byas gsum po ni rtag /'dus byas bdag gis kun stong la //
T04TD3851E:27a-49: byed pa po med skad cig ma //
T04TD3851E:27a-50: mig las skye blo rnam med cing //
T04TD3851E:27a-51: mngon sum rig pa rdul gyi tshogs //
T04TD3851E:27a-52: blo ldan zhes bya kha che yi //
T04TD3851E:27a-53: bye brag smra ba'i gzhung du bshad //
T04TD3851E:27b-0: mthong ba @27b dbang po'i yul min te //
T04TD3851E:27b-1: shes pa rnam pa bcas pa skye //
T04TD3851E:27b-2: nam mkha' mo gsham bu 'dra la //
T04TD3851E:27b-4: 'dus byas bems po yod min la //
T04TD3851E:27b-5: dus gsum dag kyang khas mi len //
T04TD3851E:27b-6: bsags pa'i gzugs med min zhes pa //
T04TD3851E:27b-7: mdo sde pa ni mkhas rnams so //
T04TD3851E:27b-8: cha shas can zhes bya med cing //
T04TD3851E:27b-9: phra rab rdul rnams med pa dang //
T04TD3851E:27b-10: so sor snang ba dmigs med dang //
T04TD3851E:27b-11: nyams su myong ba rmi lam 'dra //
T04TD3851E:27b-12: gzung dang 'dzin pa las grol ba'i //
T04TD3851E:27b-13: rnam shes dam pa'i don du yod //
T04TD3851E:27b-14: blo mtsho'i pha rol phyin pa yi //
T04TD3851E:27b-15: rnal 'byor spyod pa'i gzhung du bsgrags //
T04TD3851E:27b-16: rnam shes dam pa'i don ldan pa //
T04TD3851E:27b-17: de yang brten rnams mi 'dod de //
T04TD3851E:27b-18: gcig dang du ma'i rang bzhin dang //
T04TD3851E:27b-19: bral phyir nam mkha'i padma bzhin //
T04TD3851E:27b-20: yod min med min yod med min //
T04TD3851E:27b-21: gnyis ka'i bdag nyid kyang min pas //
T04TD3851E:27b-22: mtha' bzhi las grol dbu ma pa //
T04TD3851E:27b-23: mkhas pa rnams kyi de kho na'o //
T04TD3851E:27b-24: chos la 'bad pa med na ni //
T04TD3851E:27b-25: gang phyir de nyid mi 'grub pa //
T04TD3851E:27b-26: de phyir mkhas pas nan tan gyis //
T04TD3851E:27b-27: chos la legs par blta bar bya //
T04TD3851E:27b-28: 'jig rten mgon gyis gsungs pa yang //
T04TD3851E:27b-29: mchog tu brtsam bya min pa la //
T04TD3851E:27b-30: phyag byas nas ni brtsams la 'jug / gang gang nyan pa gus pas so //
T04TD3851E:27b-31: bsregs bcad bdar ba'i gser bzhin du //
T04TD3851E:27b-32: dge slong dag gam mkhas rnams kyis //
T04TD3851E:27b-33: yongs su brtags la nga yi bka' //
T04TD3851E:27b-34: blang bar bya yi gus phyir min //
T04TD3851E:27b-35: des na 'bad pas bla ma ni //
T04TD3851E:27b-36: yang dang yang du mchod bya zhing //
T04TD3851E:27b-37: gang phyir sems ni brtan gyur ces //
T04TD3851E:27b-38: nye bar bstan pa yongs su dri //
T04TD3851E:27b-39: gang tshe sems ni sems med pa //
T04TD3851E:27b-40: rtog pa kun nas gsal byed pa //
T04TD3851E:27b-41: de tshe sems ni gar song dang //
T04TD3851E:27b-42: gar gnas mthong bar mi 'gyur ro //
T04TD3851E:27b-43: sems ni yongs su shes pa las //
T04TD3851E:27b-45: de phyir 'bad pa'i tshul rnams ni //
T04TD3851E:27b-46: sna tshogs pa yi sems goms bya //
T04TD3851E:27b-47: yid ni gang dang gar 'gro ba //
T04TD3851E:27b-48: de dag nyid du sbyar shes bya //
T04TD3851E:27b-49: gang du g-yo zhing 'gro byed pa //
T04TD3851E:27b-50: thams cad de yi rang bzhin no //
T04TD3851E:27b-51: 'di ni bag chags bcas pa yis //
T04TD3851E:28a-0: @28a * // bag chags kyis ni khrid cing khyer //
T04TD3851E:28a-2: bag chags las ni bkri zhing bkyer //
T04TD3851E:28a-3: gang dang gang gis mi rnams kyi //
T04TD3851E:28a-4: yid ni yang dag sbyor 'gyur ba //
T04TD3851E:28a-5: sna tshogs gzugs can nor bu bzhin //
T04TD3851E:28a-6: rang bzhin de dang der 'gyur ro //
T04TD3851E:28a-7: gzhung 'di byas pas bsod nams gang //
T04TD3851E:28a-8: bzang po bdag gis bskyed pa des //
T04TD3851E:28a-9: 'jig rten ma lus sangs rgyas kyi //
T04TD3851E:28a-10: ye shes la ni gzhol bar shog / ye shes snying po kun las btus pa zhis bya ba /
T04TD3851E:28a-11: slob dpon chen po 'phags pa lha'i zhal snga nas kyis mdzad pa rdzogs so /
T04TD3851E:28a-13: // / rgya gar gyi mkhan po krishna pa dang /
